# Privacy Policy – Gynnie#3853

**Last Updated:** 8/11/2

This Privacy Policy explains how **Gynnie#3853** (Discord bot ID: 1404580551171772437, hereafter referred to as the "Bot") handles data.

## 1. Data Collection
This Bot is used exclusively by its owner and does not collect personal data from other users. Any data processed is limited to:
- Creative content, notes, and story elements provided by the owner.

## 2. Data Usage
All stored data is used solely for personal creative purposes related to the **Wolves of Aurveneth** universe.

## 3. Data Sharing
No data is shared, sold, or transferred to third parties.

## 4. Data Storage
Any data stored by the Bot exists only within the owner’s controlled environment (Discord messages, local backups, or personal storage). Discord's own data policies apply to content sent through Discord.

## 5. Security
Reasonable measures are taken to keep stored content secure. However, no method of storage or transmission is 100% secure.

## 6. Policy Updates
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Continued use of the Bot after updates constitutes acceptance of the new policy.
